        {
            "review_id": "226422911",
            "steam_id": "76561197969877947",
            "playtime_minutes": 76,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.5,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "Last time I bought/installed MS FS it came on 3 1/2\" floppies.   With the Steam Edition, there is no chasing down my kids after a move to get my stuff!   My purchases are always right THERE!   Next, I have a Logitech Extreme Pro USB joystick.  It is a glorified Wingman Extreme to my thinking.  But better!   FS X installed with my DLC in minutes, and played instantly!   It found and set up my exact joystick without any issue.  No crashes.  Even gave me scenery I wanted on first play.  I chose the Ultralight just to get familiar with the sim.  Gee I got a LOT of catching up to do!  But this is much more realistic looking and feeling.  And well worth the price!  Thanks  MS, for getting this RIGHT!"
        },
